    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bash your <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, cut down the middle lengthways, remove the <strong>tough outer layers</strong> (save them for later) and chop the<strong> softer inner core[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and roughly chop, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>peanuts</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-47-1724338543744-x200.jpg",
