      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>lemongrass outer layers</strong> from the rice and discard, then fluff the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with a fork and stir your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> through – this is your <strong>black sesame rice</strong></p>",
